I"ô<p>The Art and Design Studios (ADS) at the Office of Li Zhaozhi announced the first animated film project today. This animated film will be titled The Cat Pavilion.</p>

<p>Combining captivating stories, state-of-the-art filmmaking technologies, and art and design, The Cat Pavilion will deliver an immersive entertaining experience to audiences worldwide. This film will be around 10 minutes and released on this website, BiliBili, YouTube and other video-streaming platforms. The film will be available in Chinese, English and Spanish.</p>

<p>This film is scheduled to release in December 2022 during the 2023 Christmas break. For more information, please visit the official website of the studios at <a href="https://mrlizhaozhi.github.io/art-and-design">https://mrlizhaozhi.github.io/art-and-design</a> and of the film at <a href="https://mrlizhaozhi.github.io/art-and-design/portfolio/animation/the-cat-pavilion/">https://mrlizhaozhi.github.io/art-and-design/portfolio/animation/the-cat-pavilion/</a>.</p>
